description:
&ldquo;This bitch is not my daughter.&rdquo;

Ariel was born in the Marquis family but she was abused and abandoned by them. She ended up a miserable death filled with endless misfortune. When she woke up, she was nine years old again. In order to not repeat the miserable life, Ariel decides to have a contractual marriage with the son of the grand duke, Lakatyer, who is famous for blood and madness.

&ldquo;Good, Ariel. Now you are the Lady of this house.&rdquo;

&ldquo;But I just married yesterday&hellip;&rdquo;

&ldquo;The Grand Duchess is not here so you are the Lady of this house.&rdquo;

Ariel responds, clenching her fists, &ldquo;I will do my best.&rdquo;

&ldquo;No, you don&rsquo;t need to do your best. The house is all yours. So just think of how to enjoy it.&rdquo;

Why is everyone so nice to me?

&ldquo;Speaking of which, what are all these keys?&rdquo;

The housekeeper glanced at the keys and laughed.

&ldquo;These keys are for the treasury of the grand duke&rsquo;s family.&rdquo; Yeah? What do you&hellip;?

&lsquo;He said that I can use all of them as I please because there are all mine?&rsquo;

Ariel just barely understood the situation barely and surprised. Wait&hellip; it means he left all his treasures to me even though I&rsquo;m just ten years old? She was confused, why does she have the repository keys of this house? Will the house be fine with this?
